[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter examining the code snippets and evaluation report, I can identify the root [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause of the compilation error:[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Root Cause:** The previous patch incorrectly inserted a class declaration and LOG[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfield inside the Javadoc comment block [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m46[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m47[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which created malformed code.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe actual class declaration is at line [0m[1;36m63[0m[39m, and static fields should be declared [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter line [0m[1;36m65[0m[39m where `EMPTY_STRING` is defined.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Vulnerability Confirmation:** The RCE vulnerability exists at lines [0m[1;36m215[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m217[0m[39m where[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mObjectInputStream.readObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` deserializes untrusted data from RTF files without[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation. This is a critical security issue that must be addressed.[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Existing Error Handling Pattern:** The TextExtractor class [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m1477[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m already [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcatches TikaException/IOException from `[0m[1;35mhandleCompletedObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and records them [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvia `[0m[1;35mEmbeddedDocumentUtil.recordException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which adds exceptions to the [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`TIKA_META_EXCEPTION_WARNING` metadata field.[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Import Section Changes [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m19[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m23[0m[1;39m)[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Remove line [0m[1;36m21[0m[39m:** Delete `import java.io.ObjectInputStream;` to prevent its [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39musage[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Add after line [0m[1;36m23[0m[39m:** Insert SLF4J imports:[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```java[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  import org.slf4j.Logger;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Static Field Declaration [0m[1;39m([0m[39mAfter Line [0m[1;36m65[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Add after line [0m[1;36m65[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mimmediately after `private static final String [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mEMPTY_STRING = [0m[32m""[0m[39m;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```java[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  private static final Logger LOG = [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mLoggerFactory.getLogger[0m[1;39m([0m[39mRTFEmbObjHandler.class[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This placement is correct because:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - It's inside the actual class body [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m63[0m[39m's class declaration[0m[1;39m)[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - It's grouped with other static fields [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnear EMPTY_STRING[0m[1;39m)[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - It's in proper scope for use throughout the class[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. Replace JAVA_OBJDATA Handler [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m213[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m224[0m[1;39m)[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReplace the entire vulnerable block with secure code that:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Logs a warning** about the disabled deserialization for operator visibility[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Sets safe metadata** using generic values instead of deserializing:[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `CONTENT_TYPE_PARSER_OVERRIDE` = [0m[32m"application/octet-stream"[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstandard binary [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtype[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - `EMB_CLASS` = [0m[32m"java.lang.Object"[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mgeneric class without deserialization[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Throws TikaException** with a clear security message that will be:[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Caught by the existing error handler in TextExtractor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m1477[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Recorded in `TIKA_META_EXCEPTION_WARNING` metadata[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  - Logged for administrator awareness[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Replacement code:**[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m[39m else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mstate == EMB_STATE.JAVA_OBJDATA[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Skipping Java object deserialization for security reasons to prevent [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mRCE"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mTikaCoreProperties.CONTENT_TYPE_PARSER_OVERRIDE, [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 [0m[1;35mMediaType.OCTET_STREAM.toString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mmetadata.set[0m[1;39m([0m[39mRTFMetadata.EMB_CLASS, [0m[32m"java.lang.Object"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mTikaException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Java object deserialization is disabled for security [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mreasons "[0m[39m +[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                           [0m[32m"to prevent Remote Code Execution attacks"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This is Optimal[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Security First:** Completely eliminates the RCE vulnerability by removing [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munsafe deserialization[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Proper Compilation:** Places LOG field in correct class scope, fixing the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation error[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Follows Existing Patterns:** [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses the same error handling mechanism as other error cases [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m197[0m[1;39m)[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Leverages existing infrastructure in TextExtractor [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m1477[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Records exceptions in metadata using established Tika patterns[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Minimal Code Changes:** Only modifies the vulnerable code path without [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maffecting other functionality[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Clear Communication:** Provides warning logs and exception messages explaining[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe security decision[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Preservation of Existing Logic[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Does not modify:** OBJDATA handler [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m191[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m198[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, PICT handler [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m211[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, NADA handler [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m225[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Maintains:** The EMB_STATE state machine, metadata handling, and [0m[1;35mreset[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mworkflow[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves:** Error recording infrastructure and embedded document extraction [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor non-Java objects[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Does not break:** Existing tests for other RTF features [0m[1;39m([0m[39monly testJavaObj will[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbe affected[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Issues[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Initial RCE Issue:** Removes the dangerous `[0m[1;35mObjectInputStream.readObject[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcall entirely[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Compilation Error:** Places LOG field declaration in proper class body [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m65[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Metadata Recording:** Uses existing `TikaException` → `[0m[1;35mrecordException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpattern for proper error tracking[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Operator Visibility:** Adds WARNING-level logging so administrators know why [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeserialization is skipped[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects & Mitigation[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: testJavaObj Test Failure**[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Impact:** The test expects [0m[32m"java.lang.String"[0m[39m in EMB_CLASS and deserialized [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcontent[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** This is acceptable because the test validates dangerous [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality that must be disabled[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Note:** The test demonstrates this was an intentional feature, but security [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moverrides functionality[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Loss of Java Object Extraction**[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Impact:** RTF files with embedded serialized Java objects will no longer [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mextract object content[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** This is the intended security trade-off; the raw bytes remain [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mavailable as octet-stream[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Justification:** Arbitrary deserialization of untrusted data is a well-known [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mRCE vector that cannot be safely supported[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Metadata Contains Exception**[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Impact:** Every RTF with javaobjdata will have TIKA_META_EXCEPTION_WARNING in [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmetadata[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Mitigation:** This is correct behavior - it alerts users that the feature was [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdisabled for security[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **Benefit:** Provides audit trail of security-related processing decisions[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe pattern of throwing TikaException for security/error conditions is used [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthroughout Tika:[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m197[0m[39m: IOException caught and recorded via [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mEmbeddedDocumentUtil.recordException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Line [0m[1;36m258[0m[39m: IOException recorded via `[0m[1;35mrecordEmbeddedStreamException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- EncryptedDocumentException: Similar pattern of throwing descriptive exceptions [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor security-related issues[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix follows the same established pattern for handling situations where content[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcannot be safely processed.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                   [0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=510165;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=896888;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\
